msg":"尻up真係冇難度， 條盪x 都唔睇鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25a7ef501088b09c10fa59e19c088981618241f","tid":1800521,"uid":1727,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:08:25.000Z","msg":"仲空姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都冇撈屌啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算真係要食空中服務員條水，你都空嬸啦吓嘛"},{"pid":"ffed2f95c1eaa2e4de7c77d82be18e02c58c7eb2","tid":1800521,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:15:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>SHOP商場戰略檢討與重點</ins></strong></span> 幫手share<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong>1) 落閘就目標已達成, 可以轉場</strong></ins></span><br />\n商場落閘基本上都係因為D狗入撚哂黎, 咁達成目標 無需要再屌狗同戀戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>2) 街坊被捕個時麻煩街坊咪撚係度嘈</ins></strong></span><br />\n琴日已經有幾次係因為街坊太嘈, 個街坊大聲叫都無人聽到佢講乜, 咁樣同害9自己友無分別。一陣無名無姓無資料, 係咪想人地被消失??<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>3) 回馬槍，D狗走個時唔撚好再上前</ins></strong></span><br />\n尤其是商場入面，次撚次比人回馬槍幾次。每次都捉撚左2-3個。屌狗還屌狗, 你地係後面屌就爽, 企前面既街坊就中伏。唔好再做豬隊友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>4) 12點好撤，再留係度攬炒指數低</ins></strong></span><br />\n咁夜對政權既傷害係邊度? 個撚個都返鳩哂屋企訓教, 車又少。同玩平原戰 自殺有咩分別? 大家要記住個目標係乜野。街上又無其他路人幫你地cover, 過左12點又無車走。好似琴日MK咁, D人又話走唔撚到比狗包圍住。咪撚再要呀寶出動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">[告急] 德國人權法30號截,差22K, 用chrome簽, <br />\nchrome可以幫你翻譯做中文, <br />\n唔撚洗睇教學都識簽 洗撚睇教學咩<br />\n直接right click 轉做中文啦 好撚易之嘛</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=1bfa30bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJuUQZm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJuUQZm.png&h=76bbc9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OL5471p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOL5471p.png&h=1335725b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7f22e3b6ef18d5e1492407353bd0038ba42b1d9","tid":1800521,"uid":1977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b42e9d5d8e3ea0aa1b1ac96a55d91c062f2ee5df","tid":1800521,"uid":64345,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZSWjVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZSWjVK.jpg&h=3fcd7dd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:18:22.000Z","msg":"成個醬爆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127c0f61cba6d5ea8fbe3b00d9e0676895068196","tid":1800521,"uid":247719,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:19:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03619ac57d9f5dc845f393bf45d82001e75cafdb","tid":1800521,"uid":161365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"原來藍屍個邊好多天使<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b740940ec197985701db5a2e6861b4d2f780a3d1","tid":1800521,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c41088b85b69423320c3b2137e783ac56621239d","tid":1800521,"uid":5967,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"b42e9d5d8e3ea0aa1b1ac96a55d91c062f2ee5df","tid":1800521,"uid":64345,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZSWjVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZSWjVK.jpg&h=3fcd7dd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T09:00:49.000Z","msg":"呢隻撚樣咪係維園陀胡椒槍便衣<br />\n累撚到屯門老家比人淋油<br />\n<br />\n睇下幾時搞到比人搵埋老豆老母祭旗<br />\n正宗不孝子"},"c